data.description: MUST SEE! If you're looking for value, here it is.  One of the largest and updated units at Ely Walker for a steal of a price! Absolutely stunning loft in the heart of downtown. Unit 501 has had extensive updates and offers an open floor plan with over 1500sqft that looks out over Washington Avenue. The kitchen has been completely updated with quartz countertops, gorgeous green cabinets with glass hardware, stainless steel appliances including wine fridge. Full guest bath has updated shower and vanity with quartz countertop.  Primary bedroom suite offers a huge walk in closet (California Closet system in both bedroom closets), double vanity, updated shower and separate soaking tub. Upgraded lighting throughout unit. Walk to City Museum, Busch Stadium and MLS stadium plus all the great restaurants! 1 car secured parking in the building, storage locker in building, roof top deck and exercise room!
